5.3 Subsequent measurement of financial liabilities
</chunk>

<chunk id="645" doc_uid="ifrs-9-financial-instruments 2025 required" section_path="5.3.1" >
After initial recognition, an entity shall measure a financial liability in
accordance with paragraphs 4.2.1–4.2.2.
</chunk>

<chunk id="646" doc_uid="ifrs-9-financial-instruments 2025 required" section_path="5.3.2" >
An
entity
